premise_source_doc_sentence: Southeast Asia or Southeastern Asia is a subregion of Asia , consisting of the countries that are geographically south of China , east of India , west of New Guinea and north of Australia .
Southeast Asia consists of two geographic regions :
Mainland Southeast Asia , also known historically as Indochina , comprising Vietnam , Laos , Cambodia , Thailand , Myanmar  (  Burma  )  , and  (  West  )  Malaysia .

Maritime Southeast Asia , also known historically as the East Indies comprising Indonesia ,  (  East  )  Malaysia , Singapore , Philippines , East Timor , Brunei , Christmas Island , Andaman and Nicobar Islands , and Cocos  (  Keeling  )  Islands .
